Rhomobile Quiz
=============
A simple quiz application to test out capabilities in Rhomobile and create a native look and feel for several plattforms. 

Type of questions
 - Ask with text, multiple choice answer
 - Ask with image, multiple choice answer
 - Ask with sound, multiple choice answer
 - Ask with video, multuple choice answer
 - Ask user to rotate device
 - Ask user to walk 100 meters
 - Ask user to scan in barcode

TODO: When the user is done answering questions the answers will be posted to a backend. 

The application should work on as many devices as possible and have a look and feel that is as native as possible for each device. Use of OS checks and custom code should be kept at a minimum
